{block type="sky"}
    <h1>Upgrade to premium!</h1>
    <p>
        You can use 42goals for <strong>free</strong> and profit from all the basic features.
        Should you decide upgrading to the premium account, you will get a more advanced functionality and a warm cozy feeling of supporting 42goals.
        Below you will find a comparative table of our subscription plans:
    </p>
    
    <ul id="pricing">
        <li id="plan-free">
            <h2>Free</h2>
            <p class="price"><strong>$0/month</strong></p>
            <p>
                All basic goals types:<br /> 
                numeric, counter, boolean, time
            </p>
            <p class="sign-up">
                {if !Access::loggedIn()}
                <a href="{@home}registration/" class="button"><span><span>Sign up</span></span></a>
                {end}
            </p>
        </li>
        <li id="plan-premium">
            <h2>Premium</h2>
            <p class="price"><strong>$5/month</strong></p>
            <p>
                All basic goals types<br />
                Advanced goals types: stopwatch<br />
                Group goals by tabs<br />
		Export goal data in CSV file
                Priority support via email
            </p>
            <p class="sign-up">
                {if Access::loggedIn()}
                <a href="{@home}pay/" class="button"><span><span>Buy now</span></span></a>
                {else}
                <a href="{@home}registration/?premium" class="button"><span><span>Sign up</span></span></a>
                {end}
            </p>
        </li>
        <li id="plan-corporate">
            <h2>Corporate</h2>
            <p class="price"><strong><a href="mailto:info@42goals.com">contact us</a> for more info</strong></p>
